{
  "stem": "4247.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And aside from the impressions it gave to the non-Jews about how to look at Jews, how did it make Jews personally feel?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Was it-- was there resentment or submission?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Was there-- and when I say that, I mean really in your family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What were the reactions to this barrage of propaganda-- of your father, of your mother?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Submission.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it was definitely no, no organized resistance of any type.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was no opportunity to do that, right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was simply-- if you are in, in, in straitjacket, you cannot hit back, right?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were in straitjacket.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Look, my-- my poor father, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] towards-- you know, in '43, '44, he was, by my measure, too, he was a relatively young man.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was 59 at that time, not even 60.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took his commercial license away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His activity was reduced to nil.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't have particularly strong financial resources and, and accumulated assets to live on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that was a constant worry, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And any-- but, but psychologically, he was a broken man, right?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember him as sitting in a-- in a-- in an armchair like that and reading the paper.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was smoking cigarettes quite heavy-- smoking cigarettes and falling asleep, right?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was of no, no value as, as, as, as a-- as giving guidance to us by that time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother, who had considerably more spirit, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] did not contribute in a-- in a-- in a-- in a-- tangible way.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But always by, by, by her remarks, by her philosophy, by implied philosophy, always provided more, more hope, more, more, more sunshine.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "However, however, we knew that we are doomed.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
